        <h3 class="brow">NRGI Strategy 2020-2025</h3>
        <h1>Resource Governance for a Changing World</h1>
      </hgroup>
      <section>
        <p>The oil, gas and mining sectors have largely failed to deliver on the promise of better quality of life for the one billion people living in poverty in resource-rich countries.</p>
        <p>The Natural Resource Governance Institute works to change that.</p>
      </section>
