    <div class="base-card__body bottom-card">
      <h2 class="base-card__title"><a>navigating the energy transition</a></h2>

      <h3 class="base-card__subtitle">objective</h3>

      <p class="base-card__paragraph">Resource-rich countries advance rather than hinder the transition to cleaner energy. Countries rich in strategic minerals do not replicate mis-governance in that subsector.</p>

