    <div class="base-card__body bottom-card">
      <h2 class="base-card__title"><a>addressing corruption and "state capture"</a></h2>

      <h3 class="base-card__subtitle">objective</h3>

      <p class="base-card__paragraph">Governments and companies conduct sector operations in ways that reduce opportunities for corruption and capture, and anticorruption actors tackle extractive sector corruption more effectively.</p>

      <div class="base-card__cluster">
        <div class="cluster-box">"Corruption Risks"</div>
        <div class="cluster-box">"State capture by elites"</div>
      </div>

