</section>

<section class="text-section">
  <div class="center center--narrow">
    <p><strong>NRGI will continue to apply our expertise in activities like licensing and revenue sharing.</strong></p>
    <p>Our work will also range from improving the governance of state companies, to analyzing the critical role played by China; from identifying obligations and opportunities for private companies, to what advising governments of resource-rich countries about how to navigate the coming shift to renewable energy.</p>
  </div>
</section>

